                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "He linked the League too closely to European politics."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "He had agreed that America would pay most of the cost of the League."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "He failed to take the case for the League to the American public."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_4",
                  "content": "He ordered Democratic senators to defeat the pro-League treaty with the Lodge reservations."
